parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light on the dashboard remains illuminated
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash
the passenger side airbag deploys but the driver side airbag does not
the airbag system is repeatedly repaired but the issue persists.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, leading to the failure of airbags to deploy in the event of a crash, resulting in serious injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The airbag light on the dashboard remains illuminated
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of a crash
the airbag sensor is faulty
the seatbelt receptacle is faulty.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the traction control system can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle loses control
the traction control feature fails to work
the vehicle hits a guard rail.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat tracks can cause the seats to move unexpectedly, leading to a partial loss of control of the vehicle, which can increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The seats move forward and rearward under braking and acceleration
the seats slide forward during braking
the seats rock back and forth when stopping
the seats can move back and forth a few inches without depressing the level to move the seats.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The tightening of the passenger seat belt around the neck and chest can cause pain and shortness of breath, which can be a distraction while driving and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The passenger seat belt tightens around the passenger's neck and chest
causing pain and shortness of breath.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The location of the seat heater control on the console between the front seats can be difficult to reach while driving, which can cause distractions and increase the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The seat heater control is difficult to reach while driving
nearly causing a collision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt tensioner can cause the airbag light to come on, and the seatbelt to lock up unexpectedly, leading to discomfort, pain, and potentially, the removal of the seatbelt, which can increase the risk of injury or death in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the seatbelt locks up unexpectedly
the seatbelt does not latch properly
the seatbelt causes pain or discomfort
the seatbelt fails to unlock even when the vehicle is stopped.
